subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: The top-ranked and four-time champion Justine Henin was stretched to the limit by Katarina Srebotnik before winning, 7-5, 6-7 (6), 6-3, to reach the quarterfinals at the Dubai Championships.Second-seeded Svetlana Kuznetsova cruised past Lucie Safarova, 6-1, 6-2, and will meet unseeded Amélie Mauresmo, the 2002 champion and last year’s runner-up.
